                    <font fontName="Inter" size="8.5" isBold="false" pdfFontName="Helvetica"/>
                </textElement>
                <text><![CDATA[On behalf of the entire Diamond Events family, we are truly honoured and delighted that you are considering us to bring your most cherished celebration to life. With over two decades of unrivalled expertise in crafting extraordinary events, Diamond Events has built a legacy rooted in excellence, integrity, and an unwavering passion for perfection.]]></text>
